<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">像這樣抬頭看星星，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺很適合訓練脖子的肌肉耶──！<delay frames="40" />
<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不對，<delay20 />好像也沒那麼適合，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望能練出許多腹肌！<delay8 />
希望能練出許多腹肌！！<delay8 />
希望能練出許多腹肌！！！<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />太棒啦──！<delay20 />
天上有這麼多流星，<delay frames="30" />
總有一個能實現我的願望吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可惡──！<delay20 />流星的數量太多了啦……<delay frames="30" />
不管我怎麼數，
每次都只能<delay8 />數到五個耶！！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">每次一看到彩虹，<delay20 />
我都會很想<delay8 />衝上去耶──！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真想在彩虹上跑馬拉松啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">每次只要彩虹出現，<delay20 />
我都會朝著它的方向跑過去，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但不管我怎麼跑，<delay8 />總是都追不到……</message>
	<message label="002_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">1、<delay8 />2、<delay8 />3、<delay8 />4、<delay8 />5、<delay8 />6、<delay8 />7！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />數完了！<delay20 />今天的彩虹有7種顏色啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不知道為什麼，我每次數彩虹的顏色時，<delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />數量都會不一樣耶，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哦哦──！<delay8 />是彩虹！<delay frames="30" />而且有兩道！！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣看來，<delay8 />
一定會有好事發生啊──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />出現啦──！<delay8 />是雙彩虹！！<delay frames="40" />
一道彩虹就夠少見了，<delay8 />竟然同時出現兩道！<delay frames="30" />
真是太稀奇了！！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">正想說<delay8 />好不容易放晴了，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒想到天空中竟然出現了兩道彩虹，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺真是賺到了耶！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="004_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總覺得看著天空中<delay8 />
搖曳的極光<delay20 />，
我開始有點想睡了耶……<pageBreak /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay8 />糟了──！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是不小心在這裡睡著，<delay20 />
就算是我也會感冒的！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">極光看起來<delay8 />好像超大塊的窗簾喔──！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />到底是多巨大的傢伙在用啊？<delay20 />
我有點好奇耶<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是太神奇了……<delay20 />
極光到底是怎麼出現在空中的啊？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我真的<delay8 />完全想不通耶！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="005_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">那個飛機雲看起來<delay20 />
好像體育場的跑道喔<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好！<delay20 />我就來慢跑一下吧──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">不知道為什麼，<delay8 />我只要看到飛機雲<delay20 />
就會很想追上去！<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯……<delay20 />真的好想追上去喔──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要<delay8 />我認真起來，<delay20 />
也能跑出<delay8 />像飛機雲一樣的煙霧喔！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但現在<delay8 />還不是該認真的時候，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="006_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">月亮看起來圓滾滾的，<delay20 />好像一顆球喔……<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好，<delay20 />我決定了！<delay frames="40" />
明天就來<delay8 />精進我的球技吧──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">嗯……<delay20 />月亮表面的那個圖案，<delay frames="30" />
是不是很像什麼東西啊？<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay8 />是<tag a="110" b="11" arg="0xcd00" />嗎！？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">嘿嘿，<delay8 />月光好明亮喔！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總覺得就跟晚上的體育館一樣，<delay20 />
讓我忍不住<delay8 />興奮起來啦──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>